* Dermatologic and Cosmetic Procedures in Office Practice (2011)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elsevier.com/wps/find/bookdescription.print/725801/description#description |title=Dermatologic and Cosmetic Procedures in Office Practice |publisher=Elsevier |date=2012-05-10 |accessdate=2012-05-24}}</ref>
* The Color Atlas of Family Medicine (2008)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mhprofessional.com/product.php?isbn=0071474641 |title=McGraw-Hill: The Color Atlas of Family Medicine : Book |publisher=Mhprofessional.com |date=2008-10-27 |accessdate=2012-05-24}}</ref>
* Practical Allergy (2003)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Practical-Allergy-1e-Etan-Milgrom/dp/0323012361 |title=Practical Allergy, 1e (9780323012362): Etan Milgrom, Richard P. Usatine, Ricardo Tan, Sheldon Spector: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2012-05-24}}</ref>
* Yoga RX (2002)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Yoga-RX-Step---Step-Wellness/dp/0767907493/ref=sr_1_5?ie=UTF8&qid=1328192854&sr=8-5 |title=Yoga RX: A Step-by-Step Program to Promote Health, Wellness, and Healing for Common Ailments (9780767907491): Larry Payne, Richard P. Usatine, Merry Aronson, Rachelle Gardner: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2012-05-24}}</ref>
* Skin Surgery: A Practical Guide (1998)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.com/Skin-Surgery-Practical-Richard-Usatine/dp/0815173628 |title=Skin Surgery: A Practical Guide: Richard P. Usatine, Edward L. Tobinick, Daniel Mark Siegel: 9780815173625: Amazon.com: Books |publisher=Amazon.com |date= |accessdate=2012-05-24}}</ref>

Dr. Usatine is the co-founder and co-president of Usatine Media, LLC, which has been developing medical apps for iOS (Apple iPhone, iPad and iPod touch) as well as Android since 2010. Currently Usatine Media has many apps from such diverse areas in medicine as anatomy, family medicine, dermatology, ultrasound, emergency medicine, infectious disease and aesthetics.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://usatinemedia.com |title=Usatine Media LLC |accessdate=2012-05-24}}</ref>

